com.paypal.selion.platform.html

Class TextField

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.platform.html.AbstractElement
      • com.paypal.selion.platform.html.TextField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Clickable, Hoverable, Typeable

    public class TextField
extends AbstractElement
implements Typeable
    This class is the web element Input wrapper.

    In this class, the method 'type' is encapsulated and invokes a SeLion session to type content to the specified element.
